	<Title>
		Heart disease prevention: Does oral health matter?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Taking care of your teeth hasn&apos;t been proved a key to heart disease prevention.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Will taking care of my teeth help prevent heart disease?
	</Question>
